name: Dropbox-takephotosample
tagline: This is a simple test with DropBox JavaScript API
body:
### Welcome to DropBox-takephoto-Sample.
This page is a example of a DropBox tiny app with JavaScript API. This is my first step in DropBox, and when you have great ideas with learning DropBox API or any problem, you may share with me.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with anything? You can leave a message at hongyesoftware@gmail.com
